  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT94">
<l>meyteḷintā reñceyyār vēṟāṉār nīṟāka</l>
<l>kaiteḷintu kāṭṭik kaḷappaṭuttu paiteḷinta</l>
<l>pāmpi ṉaṇaiyā yaruḷā yaṭiyēṟku</l>
<l>vēmpuṅ kaṟiyāku mēṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You whose bed is the snake with bright hoods,</l>
<l>—who, understanding that the dissident [foes] [should] turn into ashes—</l>
<l>felled [them] in the battlefield, giving a little [help to the Pāṇḍavas]!</l>
<l rend="indent">Please be gracious to me, a servant!</l>
<l>If [one] accepts [it], even neem becomes a dish. What will those</l>
<l rend="indent">who have understood the truth not do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
